title: Jeselnik  and The Big Bad Birthday Boy
itunes:title: Jeselnik  and The Big Bad Birthday Boy
description:
Gregg turns 40 and Anthony took him to the best meal he's had in a long time. Erica went to Anthony's show live in Los Angeles this weekend and got to hang out backstage- but Gregg didn't show up. Some major headlines this week; a massive Daytona 500 crash and a tennis legend says that transgender people competing is "insane and cheating".
